{"blocks":[{"key":"95b8o","text":"Resuspend the pellet in 30-50 µl sterile 1XTE buffer.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6ebsf","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"ftefl","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3i2h3","text":"Resuspend the pellet in 50 µl sterile 1XTE buffer for surface and DCM samples. \nResuspend the pellet in 30 µl sterile 1XTE buffer for 150m, 500m, and 890m samples. ","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"d6er3","text":"Vortex and quick spin twice. Then, incubate at 40 °C for 1 hr.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ecaqh","text":"After re‐suspension, immediately quantify using PICO Green (Invitrogen).  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ffb9u","text":"If \"a\" and \"b\" both get good yields, pool \"a\" and \"b\". Then transfer half of the total volume to a 1.5 ml LoBind tube for archiving, and transfer another half to a 1.5 ml LoBind tube for working stock.
